channel.description: This song is inspired by the group clipping. And I was inspired and made a song in about two hours. It is based off of space travel and death of a crew (Not a real true story). I hope you enjoy the song and give some feedback! Any comments (SoundCloud or disco) are very much appreciated. Thanks and _[enjoy](https://soundcloud.com/whoisejoc/a-gentle-kiss-from-death)_ . ![image|500x500](upload://sQa5Pm3zp2EOT6Lipn7hoMXIp5B.jpeg)
